recipe.label: Smoked Salmon Pizza (a la Wolfgang)
ingredientLines: 1 whole side salmon, pin bones removed
2 cups warm water (105 degrees F to 115 degrees F)
5 to 5 1/2 cups unbleached all-purpose flour, plus more for dusting, preferably organic
2 tablespoons finely chopped mixed fresh herbs (dill, chervil, chives, parsley), plus more whole herbs for garnish
Kosher salt and freshly ground black pepper
Special equipment: alder woodchips, soaked in cold water for 4 hours
